---

## 🏆 Evaluation Criteria
Your project will be evaluated based on:
- **Clarity of problem statement** (10%)
- **Completeness of process mapping** (20%)
- **Functionality of automation** (40%)
- **Documentation & presentation** (20%)
- **Creativity & practicality of solution** (10%)

---

## ✅ Pro Tips for Success
- Keep your problem **small and focused** – you only have to automate part of it.
- Test your automation multiple times before submission.
- Make your diagrams **clear and neat** – presentation matters in industry.
- Use **meaningful names** for your flow, lists, and files.

---

**End of Project Brief**
